commit.message: Fixed various minor issues. This should be ready to present!
Minor bug fixes, freshening, and additions to reference.
Fixed puzzle switching issues (albeit in a sloppy way...)
All methods are bypassed if fields are invalid. Ports now display.
Inject function now works with ports, which are now implemented.
Manual (somewhat) formatted.
Added command descriptions.
Added bare reference manual.
Added jump and skip functions.
Added line highlighting! Cleaned up the "You're Winner!" thumb.
Various cleanup.
Added add and sub commands.
Basic level load functionality implemented (though I still need to use local json).
Added win confirmation, but needs a new image.
Fixed resize issue. Implented mission view and level select view.
Reset is fixed!
Reset function's buggy, but victory functionality is done.
Text area now has line numbers. Does not work with vertical scroll.
Added color markers and store field to network display.
Network maps are now stored in JSON. Sprite sheet added, and preloading fixed.
UI still looks off, but all nodes and connections are correctly drawn.
Added rudimentary network drawing functions. Did a bad thing and combined the V and MC classes.
Finally, Canvas is cooperative, and is both inserted and responds to changing main_screen sizes.
Added fonts, icons, and adjusted sidebar contents.
Implemented commandDictionary commands 'inject', 'return', and 'set'. Introduced sample network variable.
Added environment variable, and basic environment interactions (returns, updates) to commandDictionary and runner functions.
Added event to 'Run!' button, allowing the text in textarea to execute.
Command dictionary is functional! Also added a Node and Runner classes.
Sidebar contents complete, Coffeescript installed, basic Coffee/JS script made.
Basic structure implemented.
